 des Wiener Historismus sowohl kunst- als auch kulturgeschichtlich untersucht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aART / History / General.2bisacsh  aRingstraßenarchitektur, Historismus, Theophil Hansen, Christian Griepenkerl.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2015z9783110438642oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205201779423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205201779.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKAb2015